    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's exactly what i'm seeing. it's like it's hiding in the gaps of the kernel. if this is being rolled out via standard OS updates, then the people running these companies must be in on it, or at least totally compromised. they're basically turning every computer on earth into a terminal for this harvest. do you think there's any way to fight back, or is the infrastructure already too deeply compromised to even trust a clean install?",
